                "name": "Death Throes",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A slain dark champion combusts in an explosive flash that destroys its armor but not its other gear. All creatures within a 10-foot radius burst take 3d6 points of fire damage and an additional 2d6 points of piercing damage (Reflex DC 17 half). The save DC is Constitution-based. "
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Fighter Training",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "Dark champions are proficient with all simple and martial weapons and with all armor and shields. They have a base attack bonus equal to their Hit Dice and can select combat feats that have fighter levels as a prerequisite, treating their Hit Dice as their fighter level for that purpose."
            }
